ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend the course to anyone. This is an essential course to people who wants to deal with economic modeling seriously.
If you want to do micro theory, it is the course for you. I recommend the course!

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course deepened my knowledge in economic theory and I might include the term paper from the course into my dissertation.
Reading papers for the course gave me ideas for my own research.
To a great extent. It matches my interest.
